HEADWORD: Ophthalmology
<hw>Oph`thal*mol"o*gy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>'ofqalmo`s</grk> the eye + <ets>-logy</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>ophthalmologie</ets>.]</ety> <def>The science which treats of the
structure, functions, and diseases of the eye.</def>⟦br⟧
